  "text": "Membranes 2019, 10, x FOR PEER REVIEW 10 of 32 serious membrane fouling [CITATION_1] . The change of TMP is an important indicator that directly reflects the membrane fouling of an AnMBR, and the influence of HRT on TMP is shown in Figure 5 . This indicates that shorter HRT will lead to rapid increase of TMP and aggravate membrane fouling, which is not conducive to long-term stable operation of AnMBR.",
